      "text": "Cause I can't let you fuck with me no more",
      "start": 51.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 62.18000030517578,
      "text": "I wanna feel good and I feel hate from you",
      "start": 58.15999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 66.44000244140625,
      "text": "Yeah, I think I should feel like I'm in the moon",
      "start": 62.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 70.80000305175781,
      "text": "I've loved you since the day I met you, still fucking new",
      "start": 66.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 76.30000305175781,
      "text": "But you hate me and I don't know what else I can prove",
      "start": 71.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 80.80000305175781,
      "text": "Fuck, what else is there to do?",
      "start": 77.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 84.9000015258789,
      "text": "Ooh, I gave you life, gave you reasons to rhyme",
      "start": 81
    },
    {
      "end": 87.22000122070312,
      "text": "Made you art into the night",
      "start": 84.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 91.62000274658203,
      "text": "I loved every way you used to fucking fight at me",
      "start": 87.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 96.0199966430664,
      "text": "Oh, come on, the lightning in between us, red line",
      "start": 92.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 98.76000213623047,
      "text": "Tether, bitch, you're better than this, ay",
      "start": 96.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 103.76000213623047,
      "text": "I know it's a little rough",
      "start": 99.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 108.04000091552734,
      "text": "I know, yeah, you think you're tough",
      "start": 104.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 110.27999877929688,
      "text": "But inside you're falling, crumbling",
      "start": 108.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 112,
      "text": "You know that he's mine",
      "start": 110.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 114.95999908447266,
      "text": "You know that we've been down this line",
      "start": 112
    },
    {
      "end": 118.26000213623047,
      "text": "A thousand times",
      "start": 115.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 124.5,
      "text": "We've been down this ride a thousand times",
      "start": 118.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 129.67999267578125,
      "text": "Stop hating that you know",
      "start": 126.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 133.3000030517578,
      "text": "You're different, better, better than this, yeah",
      "start": 129.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 134.6999969482422,
      "text": "I wanna feel good",
      "start": 133.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 136.97999572753906,
      "text": "I don't wanna feel your pain",
      "start": 134.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 138.86000061035156,
      "text": "But I meant I wanna feel good",
      "start": 136.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 141.22000122070312,
      "text": "So I'm gonna stop screaming your name",
      "start": 138.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 143.82000732421875,
      "text": "I'm gonna stop shouting from the buildings",
      "start": 141.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 146.17999267578125,
      "text": "And maybe you know and maybe you'll miss me",
      "start": 143.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 149.6199951171875,
      "text": "Maybe you understand how much you are my queen",
      "start": 146.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 150.83999633789062,
      "text": "Just listen",
      "start": 149.82000732421875
    }
